* Advanced test data factory patterns
* Parallel test execution optimization
* Custom Allure reporters for detailed insights
* Performance and load testing integration
* Visual regression testing

---

## Summary

This framework is designed to be **clean, scalable, and production-ready** while remaining easy to understand. It combines **UI automation, E2E testing, and API testing** with MongoDB integration for comprehensive test automation. The architecture follows industry conventions used in mature Playwright automation projects and is suitable for real-world applications as well as technical interviews. The role-based test organization and service layer architecture make it easy to scale tests across multiple user personas and system interactions.